rComments: This is a tough course that I was really dreading but Dr. Gagosz did a pretty good job of explaining the concepts in a way that we could understand. Go to office hours!! He takes the time to reexplain concepts. Do all the practice problems as well and previous exams. Exams are kinda tricky but he only counted our best midterm and final

A great prof who will go the extra mile to make sure you succeed. He is always there to help you with your many questions, and he is very clear of what he expects from you. He puts a lot of extra exercises on blackboard, make sure to do them and you will succeed easily.

rComments: Excelent Prof, his tests were tough, however he is very clear on what he wants and explicitly tells you in class.
